Monster: Hanged Man (PDEF 2 MDEF 4) (Last on fifth turn AI)
    - Silent Arrows: Magical attack, 50% chance to inflict seal (MATK - 30%), hits all enemies
    - Hang: Inflict trap for 3 turns
    - Spell Shield: Restore health to an ally and grant them Barrier
    - Free Man: Suicides and deals half remaining HP as damage, happens on 5th turn
Monster: Dire Greyhide (Last at 60%)
